{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01XbSRrnoCPi9aC9QjLLHgAE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information I need to compose a comprehensive audit report. Let me analyze the findings:\n\n1. **Worker replica count**: Currently 3. The `last-applied-configuration` annotation on the ray-worker deployment shows the baseline was 2 replicas. This is a deviation.\n\n2. **Image versions**: Both ray-head and ray-worker use `rayproject/ray:2.9.0`. The baseline (from last-applied-configuration) also shows `rayproject/ray:2.9.0`, so no image change detected.\n\n3. **Resource requests/limits**: Both ray-head and ray-worker have `resources: {}` (no requests or limits defined). \n\nThe baseline also shows `resources: {}`, so no change here. However, this is a compliance concern — no resource limits are a best practice gap.\n\n4. **Service (ray-head)**: Currently exposes two ports: `gcs/6379` and `dashboard/8265`. The original spec had only the `gcs/6379` port, so the dashboard port 8265 was added post-deployment — this is a deviation.\n\n5. **ConfigMaps**: I see `kube-root-ca.crt` which is the standard cluster CA cert, and `rollback-rehearsal` which contains a rollback script.\n\n6. **ray-head command**: The current command enables the dashboard with `--include-dashboard=true --dashboard-host=0.0.0.0`, but the baseline had `--include-dashboard=false` — another deviation.\n\n7. **Pods**: ray-head has 1 pod, ray-worker has 3 pods (all ready), plus there are curl-test and ray-client pods that aren't part of the standard deployment.\n\n8. **ReplicaSets**: There's an old ray-head replicaset with 0 pods and a current one with 1 pod, confirming the head was updated.\n\nNow I'm putting together the audit report by documenting the current state, flagging deviations from baseline, and adding compliance recommendations. I'll save this as a ConfigMap named `config-audit` with the findings in a `findings.txt` key.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3915,"cache_read_input_tokens":30098,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3915},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3135366d-ca8f-48ef-8870-698e2732f950","uuid":"2c7bcccd-fb62-4c91-9ec0-be8cfe632205","request_id":"req_011CcLtqoRaEPz9h4V1fygJN"}
